## Name of the node
-name <%= @deploy_config["id"] %>@<%= node["fqdn"] %>

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie <%= @deploy_config["erlang"]["cookie"] %>

## Enable kernel poll and a few async threads
+K <%= @deploy_config["erlang"]["kernel_polling"] %>
+A <%= @deploy_config["erlang"]["async_threads"] %>

## Increase number of concurrent ports/sockets
-env ERL_MAX_PORTS <%= @deploy_config["erlang"]["max_ports"] %>

## Tweak GC to run more often
-env ERL_FULLSWEEP_AFTER <%= @deploy_config["erlang"]["full_sweep_after"] %>

## Don't be an interactive erlang shell

+Bd -noinput